        "words": "也要當個她眼中的好大哥喔。",
        "unit_id": 190011
    },
    {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "name": "愛梅斯",
        "words": "\n就這樣啦。",
        "unit_id": 190011
    },
    {
        "type": "background",
